track.annotation: Gerundino Fernández negra 1987 flamenco guitar. As a tribute to Rafael Cortés free Tabs can be downloaded on our site https://www.lasonanta.eu/en/guitarras-flamencas/gerundino-fernandez-flamenco-guitar-1987.html The more subscribers we get, the more Free Flamenco guitar lessons and Free Tabs we will publish. To subscribe to our Free Flamenco Guitar Lessons, please go to https://www.lasonanta.eu/en/la-sonanta-mailing-list If you want to know and feel how this Gerundino looks and sounds like, we invite you to watch and enjoy the included Free Flamenco guitar video lesson by our maestro Rezar Dominguez. This Free Flamenco guitar lesson consists of an intro enabling you to feel the sound and playability of this Gerundino, as well as a beautiful tremelo of Del Hoy al Ayer from Rafael Cortés.
